RESTAURANT-BILLING

THIS IS A JAVA PROJECT IMPLEMENTING BASIC CONCEPTS DEVELOPED AS A PART OF MY HIGH SCHOOL JAVA CIRICULLUM. 
SOFTWARE REQUIRED-ANY JAVA IDE[PROJECT WAS MADE USING BLUEJ]

OVERVIEW


This project is a basic restaurant billing system .
The modules contained are : MENU , billing interface.
The interface is developed for the cashier where he/she selects items from the menu after which , the bill is automatically generated.

SOFTWARE
The code was developed using BLUEJ IDE and any similar developement environments can be used to run the project.

